description: Welcome home to 1511 Forest Bend! With impeccable finishes, this story-book brick home  is move in ready. Per seller, upgrades made in 2022 include refreshed hardwood floors, new carpet, new  interior and exterior paint, designer lighting, new AC unit, new window screens, new electrical panel and so  much more. This former Greatwood Trails model for Village builders has a fabulous open layout that boasts 4  beds with the Primary Suite down, 3.5 baths, a chef's kitchen with white cabinets and granite counters, formal  dining room, game room, an office and an oversized garage. The beautifully landscaped backyard is perfect  for entertaining or just relaxing on the patio. The Greatwood community offers an amazing lifestyle with  pools, playgrounds, walking trails, tennis courts and A-rated schools. Showings start at first Open House, Saturday, April 16, 1-4 pm.
